headline: Jacobs to Design Florida Water Treatment Plant Upgrades for PFAS Removal
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was selected by the City of Boynton Beach in South Florida to evaluate and design upgrades at two water treatment plants to remove per- and polyfluoroalkyl substances (PFAS) from the city's groundwater supplies to comply with new U.S. federal drinking water regulations.
